type using--> i (start typing before the highlighted cursor) or--> a (start typing after the highlighted text)
escape inser mode--> esc
show line number-->  :set number
hide line numebr--> :set number!


search a text-->  /text + enter
next occurance--> n
previous occurance--> N


//backward direction
search a text-->  ?text + enter
previous occurance--> n
next occurance--> N


move to the begining of the file--> gg
move to the end of the file-->G
move forward one word--> w
move backward one word--> b
begining of the line-->0



"DELETE TEXTS"

delete current char in normal mode--> x
delete char which is left to the cursor, so go to the writing mode(i) and--> backspace

delete current line--> d
delete current word--> dw
delete till the beginning of the line--> d0
delete till the end of the line--> d$
delete till the start of the file--> dgg
delete till the end of the file--> dG


delete previous word: go to insert mode and--> ctrl+w

undo the previous operation--> u
redo the previous operation--> ctrl+r


copy current line--> yy
select multiple texts--> go into visual mode first--> v , then move cursor using up/down arrow or 'hjkl' after selecting click--> y
highlight complete line--> V
paste text after current line--> p
paste text in current line--> P
highlight by columns--> ctrl+v


exit current tab--> :q
exit all tab--> :qa




